DESCRIPTION:Action Plan\n\nGeneral Strategies\n- Establish cross-functional
  visibility into supply chain risks\n- Prioritize resilience and continuit
 y planning\n- Strengthen vendor communication and performance tracking\n\n
 Immediate Actions\n- Identify current critical supply constraints\n- Valid
 ate inventory levels and backlog exposure\n- Confirm owners for each ident
 ified issue\n\nShort-Term Actions (1–3 weeks)\n- Develop mitigation plan
 s for top constraints\n- Align with procurement and logistics on near-term
  adjustments\n- Review progress weekly and adjust actions as needed\n\nOng
 oing Actions\n- Maintain a rolling risk register\n- Monitor KPIs and suppl
 ier performance trends\n- Incorporate lessons learned into standard operat
 ing practices\nThis invite was sent by Copilot on behalf of Mackiewicz\, B
 rett [JJCUS]\n____________________________________________________________
